__e: My whole life, you taught me to be careful, to keep moving, always one step ahead of Savage, but after tracking you for 4,000 years, he'd gotten good.
I've noticed as long as I've been in the bush, you've been behind my butt.
Someone's closing in on us, and at least for her sake, I have to find out what they know.
Clicks his heels three times, goes back to Kansas, I suppose.
If any of us stops a bullet, before we die... we're going to come to you, click our heels together and ask stiffly...
If you need anything, just... tap your heels together three times, okay?
